data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614687\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mux1665702611074.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mux1665702611074.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mux1665702611074.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mux1665702611074\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The \n                                BorderColor property displays a border of the specified color around the area frame or entity. It is applicable only if the \n                                BorderType property is <code class=\"ph codeph\">flat</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mux1665702611074__topic_d102332e1_d102333e1_d102334e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mux1665702611074__p_d102335e1_d102336e1_d102337e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n            \n                                 BorderColor\n                                 <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"mux1665702611074__section_w751ab1b5b3_w752ab1b5_w753ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mux1665702611074__p_d102338e1_d102339e1_d102340e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"BorderColor=#505050\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"mux1665702611074__section_w754ab1b5b5_w755ab1b5_w756ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mux1665702611074__d5952e17\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mux1665702611074__d5952e17__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mux1665702611074__d5952e17__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mux1665702611074__d5952e17__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mux1665702611074__d5952e17__entry__2\">Name of a web color or system color. For more\n                        information, see the \"Standard Colors\" topic.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mux1665702611074__d5952e17__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mux1665702611074__d5952e17__entry__2\">Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of\n                        a color. For example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">#D90E1A</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mux1665702611074__d5952e17__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">RGBColor</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mux1665702611074__d5952e17__entry__2\">RGB (Red Green Blue) numeric values in the form\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">R</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">G</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">B</var>. For example <code class=\"ph codeph\">255,0,0</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mux1665702611074__section_f4w_zkt_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d860072e173\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mux1665702611074__table_d12056e1_d12057e1_d12058e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes for entities, No for area frames</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n                         BorderColor is applicable only if\n                           <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cys1665702610904.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cys1665702610904.html\" title=\"The BorderType property is used to display a flat or grooved border around an area frame, grid, or the default entity widget.\">BorderType</a> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">flat</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mux1665702611074__section_gs1_clt_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d860072e231\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mux1665702611074__p_d102347e1_d102348e1_d102349e1\">For the entity widget, this property can be set in\n            ProcScript using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entityProperties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curEntProperties</span> commands.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mux1665702611074__pre_f3p_flt_vwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">putitem/id vProperties,\"BorderType\",\"flat\"\nputitem/id vProperties,\"BorderColor\",\"purple\"\nputitem/id vProperties,\"BorderRadius\",\"20px\"\n$entityproperties(ORDER.SALES)=vProperties</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"mux1665702611074__fig_d102350e1_d102351e1_d102352e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Result</figcaption>\n<br/><img alt=\"Result\" class=\"image\" id=\"mux1665702611074__image_jff_hlt_vwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/flatentityframerounded.png?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mux1665702611074__section_q1d_3lt_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d860072e262\">Example: Setting in Initialization File</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mux1665702611074__p_d102359e1_d102360e1_d102361e1\">For area frames, you can specify this property on\n            the basis of frame names in the [areaframes] section of the <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span>.\n            It is not possible to set this property in the Uniface IDE. For more information, see\n               <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sra1665702688552.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sra1665702688552.html\" title=\"The [areaframes] section of the initialization file contains logical widget definitions for frames in Form components.\">[areaframes]</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mux1665702611074__pre_aq1_llt_vwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[areaframes]\nframe_basic=uframe(bordertype=flat;bordercolor=red)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mux1665702611074__section_ucf_mlt_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d860072e284\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"mux1665702611074__ul_mfv_mlt_vwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mux1665702611074__li_d41444e1_d41445e1_d41446e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ujj1665702610581.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ujj1665702610581.html\" title=\"Area frames are objects that can be used to group or separate the contents of a Form component.\">Area Frames and Lines</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mux1665702611074__li_d41447e1_d41448e1_d41449e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iic1718342502908.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iic1718342502908.html\" title=\"The udefentity widget is the default widget for entities in form components. It is a multi-occurrence list, with a minimum of one occurrence, in which fields can be freely arranged. Uniface provides a default logical widget called DefEntity that is mapped to this widget.\">udefentity (Default Entity Widget )</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614687\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614687\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Border Color (BorderColor) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The BorderColor property displays a border of the specified color around the area frame or entity. It is applicable only if the BorderType property is flat . \" BorderColor = ColorName | HexColorNumber \" Example: \"BorderColor=#505050\" Value Description ColorName Name of a web color or system color. For more information, see the \"Standard Colors\" topic. HexColorNumber Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of a color. For example: #D90E1A . RGBColor RGB (Red Green Blue) numeric values in the form R , G , B . For example 255,0,0 Usage Dynamic? Yes for entities, No for area frames Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: BorderColor is applicable only if BorderType is flat . Example: Setting in ProcScript For the entity widget, this property can be set in ProcScript using the $entityProperties or $curEntProperties commands. putitem/id vProperties,\"BorderType\",\"flat\" putitem/id vProperties,\"BorderColor\",\"purple\" putitem/id vProperties,\"BorderRadius\",\"20px\" $entityproperties(ORDER.SALES)=vProperties Copy Figure 1. Result Example: Setting in Initialization File For area frames, you can specify this property on the basis of frame names in the [areaframes] section of the .ini . It is not possible to set this property in the Uniface IDE. For more information, see [areaframes] . [areaframes] frame_basic=uframe(bordertype=flat;bordercolor=red) Copy Applies To Area Frames and Lines udefentity (Default Entity Widget ) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}